<h1 id="installation">Installation</h1>

<p><a href="https://github.com/menubar-apps/PullBar/releases/latest/download/pullBar.zip">Download</a> the latest release, extract it and drag-and-drop to the Application folder.</p>

<p>Then <a href="https://github.com/settings/tokens/new?scopes=repo">generate</a> a github access token and paste it in the application preferences with your github username:</p>

<p align="center">
  <img width="612" alt="Screen Shot 2022-01-01 at 5 33 28 PM" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/9363150/147861494-c3803e40-309f-4b5b-8098-51c7d747db52.png" />
</p>
